        {
            "title": "Alphabet的AI晶片被譽為「獨門秘籍」 或可為其創收近萬億美元",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"592\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/vJAEZL02iNWgIx0c7.l4OA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU5MjtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/7a754fd81c5e0742634d748a5c563b37\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:Alphabet;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/Alphabet\">Alphabet</a> Inc.的投資者日益確信，該公司的晶片業務將成為其未來收入的重要成長引擎。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Alphabet的張量處理單元(TPU)晶片所取得的成功，是其股價在第四季度飆升31%的主要原因，該漲幅在標普500指數成分股中位列第十。TPU向來被公司內部視為核心優勢，加速了其雲計算業務的成長。但市場正日益看好Alphabet可向第三方銷售該晶片的前景，從而有望為其開闢一條新的收入渠道，最終可能價值近萬億美元。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-2ee889b0-ad19-32d9-8a91-e86bb879e96a-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"592\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/fYIAC5YfyyGiUcLe_5vq1Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU5MjtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/1c325f7dfcd785ca60e91c3b0725deeb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「如果企業希望在輝達之外實現多元化，TPU是一個好途徑，這意味著有充分理由感到樂觀，」DA Davidson科技研究主管Gil Luria表示。「該晶片業務最終的價值可能超過谷歌雲。但即便不對外銷售晶片，更優質的晶片也能帶來更優質、更高效的雲服務。」</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Luria預計，若Alphabet認真推進TPU銷售，數年內有望占據人工智能市場20%的占有率，成為約9000億美元的一項業務。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Alphabet未回應置評請求。輝達的一位發言人引述CEO黃仁勳近期關於公司競爭優勢的表態：「企業間的競爭本質上是團隊間的較量。而全球真正能卓越構建如此複雜產品的團隊屈指可數。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">TPU是應用專用集成電路(ASIC)晶片，為特定用途定制設計，在Alphabet的場景下，應用於加速機器學習。此類晶片不如輝達生產的晶片靈活，但成本更低，在投資者紛紛質疑人工智能相關支出之際，成為了一項切實的優勢。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「輝達晶片價格高得多且難以獲取，但若能使用ASIC晶片，Alphabet正是最佳選擇，而且迄今為止引領該市場，」Homestead Advisers股票投資組合經理Mark Iong表示。「雖然它不會控制整個市場，但它是該股的獨門秘籍。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「Alphabet是唯一一家在人工智能各個層面都具有領先地位的公司，」Iong指出，他列舉了Gemini、谷歌雲、TPU以及其他多個領域。「這賦予了它極大優勢。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Alphabet’s AI Chips Are a Potential $900 Billion ‘Secret Sauce’</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Subrat Patnaik、David Watkins.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/alphabet%E7%9A%84ai%E6%99%B6%E7%89%87%E8%A2%AB%E8%AD%BD%E7%82%BA-%E7%8D%A8%E9%96%80%E7%A7%98%E7%B1%8D-%E6%88%96%E5%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E5%85%B6%E5%89%B5%E6%94%B6%E8%BF%91%E8%90%AC%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83-115717465.html",
